Guillaume Cottenceau, <gcottenc at altern dot org>, 		85% gui, 30% engine, 5% tools
Pascal Garcia, <pgarcia@ens.insa-rennes.fr>, 		100% hexagonal algorithms
Gaetan Le Guelvouit, <gaetan@mail.dotcom.com>, 		design
Yacine Zemali, <yzemali@ens.insa-rennes.fr>, 		5% gui
